natlang.rdg.discourse
Class DiscourseHistory

java.lang.Object
  natlang.rdg.discourse.DiscourseHistory
public class DiscourseHistory
extends java.lang.Object

A history containing all plot elements mentioned sofar Is used to detect repetition, add discourse markers and repeat information if a certain entity has not been mentioned for a long time

addAlso

public boolean addAlso(PlotElement pe1,
                       PlotElement pe2)
Compares two plot elements and checks if they satisfy the requirements for adding 'also': - the plot elements differ in only one argument - the plot elements differ in two arguments and these arguments have been swapped Additional requirement: - if the plot elements differ in only one argument AND this argument is the name of the action: only add the cue word if the plot elements happen at the same time!

Parameters:
pe1 - first plot element
pe2 - second plot element
Returns:
a boolean indicating whether the cue word 'also' should be added
